g.text: Microsoft 365 F3 includes Windows 10 E3except Long Term Servicing Channel (LTSC) and Microsoft Desktop Optimization Pack (MDOP).

Limitations: ·Users cannot be administrators. ·No Skype desktop or app sharing. ·Cannot schedule Skype meetings. ·No access to productivity servers. ·No Outlook Desktop access. ·No Voicemail. ·No OneDrive for Business sync.
